OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJust 10% Welsh government  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff in office each day   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Only one in 10 Welsh government staff  
OL,6, are currently working in the office    
OL,7, every day.                             
OL,9,FWith so many civil servants working    
OL,10,Ffrom home, the Welsh government is     
OL,11,Faiming to offer space in its 10 offices
OL,12,Fto other public sector workers.        
OL,14,FIt said its vision is to "maximise the 
OL,15,Fbenefits of office, remote and hybrid  
OL,16,Fworking".                              
OL,18,FBut Welsh Conservatives said the       
OL,19,Fmajority of Welsh civil servants should
OL,20,Fnot be working from home.              
